name: Program Trap (V)
Lore: 'Imperial slicers imbed a secret command in a droid''s primary performance banks. A predetermined trigger causes a power overload, destroying the droid and anything nearby.',
Text: 'Deploy on opponent''s capital or [Independent] starship.  Starship is power -2, and its gametext (except related to capacity, immunity, and identity and ability of permanent pilots) is canceled.',
